content:
Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Einstein Discovery allows you to Set Up Einstein Discovery, Get Started Using Einstein Discovery, Build Models in Einstein Discovery, Manage and Deploy Models in Einstein Discovery.

About Model Evaluation: Evaluate Model Quality, Metrics for Numeric Use Cases, Metrics for Binary Classification Use Cases. In Binary Classification Use Cases, view the Overview Tab, Model Evaluation Tab, Overall Performance Tab, Gain and Lift Charts, Cross-Validation Tab, Coefficients Tab, Threshold Evaluation, Prediction Examination Tab.

You can View the R Code and Compare Models. Deploy Models and Manage Prediction Definitions and Models. Predict & Improve Outcomes. Decision Optimization (Beta) is also available.

Navigate to the Coefficients Tab by clicking Model Evaluation then Coefficients in Performance. 

Metrics on the Coefficients Tab include:

* Number of Variables
* Number of Variables Including Interactions
* Intercept
* Value
* Coefficient: a number representing the impact an explanatory variable has on the outcome variable.
* Scaled Importance

You can filter the list, download CSV to download coefficient values.
title: Understanding Coefficients Tab in Einstein Discovery
